## Some of What's Possible

At this point, we've covered 80% of what you'd normally need. **{gt}** can do far more than what we've covered, so let's explore some of the possibilities. Here's a quick gallery of advanced techniquies. You don't need to master these (at leaset, I haven't!), but if a use case arises, between the docs and Copilot, you'll figure it out.

